    </style><h1>MCMC Post-hoc Analysis: 28 sequences</h2>
<p>Samples were created by the following command line:<p><b>command line:</b> /home/bdredeli/local/bin/bali-phy /home/bdredeli/local/share/bali-phy/examples/Globins/few.fasta --smodel DP[6] --name few-DP6</p>
<p><b>directory:</b> /brc_share/brc/bdredeli/bdredeli/Globins</p>
<h2 name="data">Data</h2>
<table class="backlit">
<tr><th>Partition</th><th>Sequences</th><th>Lengths</th><th>Substitution&nbsp;Model</th><th>Indel&nbsp;Model</th></tr>
<tr>
 <td>1</td>
 <td>~/local/share/bali-phy/examples/Globins/few.fasta</td>
 <td>141 - 190 Amino-Acids</td>
 <td>[WAG * pi] + rate~Dirichlet[6]</td>
 <td>fragment-based indels + T [HMM]</td>
</tr>
</table>
